The paper deals with analyzing performance using a neural network with particle swarm optimization. This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. The use of particle swarm optimization also suggests that the paper may fall under the category of computational intelligence, which is covered by cs.NE. The paper also deals with data analysis and feature selection, which may fall under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with the performance of lecturers in academic institutions, which may fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
